HEADWORD: Primeness
<hw>Prime"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The quality or state
of being first.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The quality or state of being prime, or
excellent.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Primer</ent>⟦br⟧
